snippet.title: C64 Game: Cosmic Convoy
snippet.description: Interesting idea and not a bad game for 1983. The ships resemble the Discovery from 2001: A Space Odyssey. Created by Andy Walker (nakedly raw) with sounds by Mark Buttery (murky batter).
